strings.Value: "When I stayed in village, I saw nothing. With you, Nok-Nok sees more during one day than during the whole life!"
"That's why goblin king would never become a Hero. He sees nothing beyond his hind!"
"I came from a tribe of nomads. I saw much when I lived with them. — Although not as much as I saw once I set off into the world..."
